<topic id="results-view">
  <title>Results View</title>
  <prolog>
    <metadata>
      <keywords>
        <indexterm>Results view</indexterm>
      </keywords>
    </metadata>
  </prolog>
  <body>
    <p id="p_ibw_bgk_54b">The <uicontrol>Results</uicontrol> view displays the messages generated as a result of user
      actions such as validations, transformations, search operations, and others. Each message is a
      link to the location related to the event that triggered the message. Double-clicking a
      message opens the file containing the location and positions the cursor at the location
      offset. The <uicontrol>Results</uicontrol> view is automatically opened when certain actions
      generate result messages. By default, the view normally opens at the bottom of the editor, but
      it is <xref keyref="glossentry_dockable"><term>dockable</term></xref>, so it can be moved to
      another UI location alongside other side views.<note type="tip"
        product="author developer editor" id="note_jbw_bgk_54b">To shift focus to the open <uicontrol>Results</uicontrol>
        view without using the mouse, there is an action in the <menucascade>
          <uicontrol>Window</uicontrol>
          <uicontrol>Results</uicontrol>
        </menucascade> menu called <uicontrol>Focus Results</uicontrol> that can be used for this
        purpose and you can <xref
          href="preferences-menu-shortcut-keys.dita#preferences-menu-shortcut-keys">assign a
          keyboard shortcut</xref> to this action.</note></p>
    <p id="p_kbw_bgk_54b">The actions that contribute messages to this view include:<ul id="ul_lbw_bgk_54b">
        <li id="li_mbw_bgk_54b" irina="irina"><xref
            href="validation-actions-in-user-interface.dita#validation-actions-in-user-interface"
            format="dita"><uicontrol>Validation</uicontrol> actions</xref></li>
        <li id="li_nbw_bgk_54b" irina="irina"><xref href="transforming-documents.dita#transforming-documents" format="dita"
              ><uicontrol>Transformation</uicontrol> actions</xref></li>
        <li id="li_obw_bgk_54b" irina="irina"><xref href="spell-check-in-files.dita#spell-check-in-files" format="dita"
              ><uicontrol>Check Spelling in Files</uicontrol> action</xref></li>
        <li id="li_pbw_bgk_54b" irina="irina"><ph product="editor author developer"><uicontrol>Find All</uicontrol> action from the
              <xref href="find-replace-dialog.dita#find-replace-dialog" format="dita"
                ><uicontrol>Find/Replace</uicontrol> dialog box</xref></ph></li>
        <li id="li_qbw_bgk_54b" irina="irina"><ph product="editor author developer"><xref
              href="find-and-replace-text-in-files.dita#find-and-replace-text-in-files"
              format="dita"><uicontrol>Find/Replace in Files</uicontrol> dialog box</xref></ph></li>
        <li product="editor editorEclipse developer developerEclipse" id="li_rbw_bgk_54b" irina="irina"><xref
            href="find-xslt-references-and-declarations.dita#find-xslt-references-and-declarations"
            format="dita"><uicontrol>Search References</uicontrol> action</xref></li>
        <li product="editor author developer" id="li_sbw_bgk_54b" irina="irina"><xref href="xpath-toolbar.dita#xpath-toolbar"
            format="dita">XPath expression results</xref></li>
        <li id="li_tbw_bgk_54b" irina="irina"><xref href="executing-sql-statements.dita#executing-sql-statements" format="dita">SQL
            results</xref></li>
      </ul></p>
    <p id="p_ubw_bgk_54b">
      <fig id="figure-validation-errors-editor" product="editor author developer">
        <title>Results View</title>
        <image href="../img/sa_results_view.png"/>
      </fig>
    </p>
    <p id="p_vbw_bgk_54b">
      <fig id="figure-validation-errors-editorEclipse"
        product="editorEclipse authorEclipse developerEclipse">
        <title>Results View</title>
        <image href="../img/ec_results_view.png"/>
      </fig>
    </p>
    <section id="results_view_toolbar_actions">
      <title>Results View Toolbar Actions</title>
      <p id="p_wbw_bgk_54b">The view includes a toolbar with the following actions:</p>
      <p id="p_xbw_bgk_54b">
        <dl id="dl_ybw_bgk_54b">
          <dlentry product="author developer editor" id="dlentry_zbw_bgk_54b">
            <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/Settings16.png" id="image_bmd_x5z_gf"
                  placement="inline"/>Settings</uicontrol> drop-down menu</dt>
            <dd>
              <p id="p_acw_bgk_54b">This drop-down menu also includes the following options:<dl id="dl_bcw_bgk_54b">
                  <dlentry id="dlentry_ccw_bgk_54b">
                    <dt>Group by "Severity"</dt>
                    <dd>Groups the results based upon the severity of the validation issues.</dd>
                  </dlentry>
                  <dlentry id="dlentry_dcw_bgk_54b">
                    <dt>Group by "Resource"</dt>
                    <dd>Groups the results based upon the type of resource.</dd>
                  </dlentry>
                  <dlentry id="dlentry_ecw_bgk_54b">
                    <dt>Group by "System ID"</dt>
                    <dd>Groups the results based upon the system ID of the resource.</dd>
                  </dlentry>
                  <dlentry id="dlentry_fcw_bgk_54b">
                    <dt>Group by "Operation description"</dt>
                    <dd>Groups the results based upon the description of the validation issue.</dd>
                  </dlentry>
                  <dlentry conkeyref="reusables-editing-documents/ungroup-all-dlentry" id="dlentry_gcw_bgk_54b">
                    <dt/>
                    <dd/>
                  </dlentry>
                  <dlentry conkeyref="reusables-editing-documents/show-columns-dlentry" id="dlentry_hcw_bgk_54b">
                    <dt/>
                    <dd/>
                  </dlentry>
                  <dlentry conkeyref="reusables-editing-documents/restore-defaults-dlentry" id="dlentry_icw_bgk_54b">
                    <dt/>
                    <dd/>
                  </dlentry>
                  <dlentry id="dlentry_jcw_bgk_54b">
                    <dt><uicontrol>Include problem ID in description</uicontrol></dt>
                    <dd>If this option is selected, validation issues will include the problem ID
                      (as provided by the validation engine) in the
                        <uicontrol>Description</uicontrol> column.</dd>
                  </dlentry>
                  <dlentry id="dlentry_ymz_kvz_54b">
                    <dt><uicontrol>Show Ignored Problems</uicontrol></dt>
                    <dd>If you have <xref href="ignore-quick-fixes.dita">ignored validation
                        problems</xref>, you can deselect this option to hide the ignored problems.
                      Likewise, you can select this option to show the ignored problems.</dd>
                  </dlentry>
                </dl></p>
            </dd>
          </dlentry>
          <dlentry product="author developer editor" id="dlentry_kcw_bgk_54b">
            <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/HighlightAll16.png" id="image_vkx_wv4_5r"/>Highlight
                all results in editor</uicontrol></dt>
            <dd><ph keyref="product"/> highlights all matches obtained after executing an XPath
              expression, or performing one of the following operations: <uicontrol>Find
                All</uicontrol>, <uicontrol>Find in Files</uicontrol>, <uicontrol>Search
                References</uicontrol>, and <uicontrol>Search Declarations</uicontrol>. Click
                <b>Highlight all results in editor</b> again to turn off highlighting. <note
                id="note_lcw_bgk_54b">To customize highlighting behavior, <ph
                  conkeyref="reusables-preferences-pages/open-the-preferences-page"/> and go to <menucascade>
                  <uicontrol>Editor</uicontrol>
                  <uicontrol>Highlights category</uicontrol>
                </menucascade>. You can do the following customizations:<ul id="ul_mcw_bgk_54b">
                  <li id="li_ncw_bgk_54b" irina="irina">Set a specific color of the highlights depending on the
                    type of action you make. </li>
                  <li id="li_ocw_bgk_54b" irina="irina">Set a maximum number of highlights that the application
                    displays at any given time. </li>
                </ul></note></dd>
          </dlentry>
          <dlentry product="authorEclipse developerEclipse editorEclipse" id="dlentry_pcw_bgk_54b">
            <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/DependencesHierarchy16.png" id="image_ey5_wz4_5r"
                />Grouping Mode</uicontrol> toggle options</dt>
            <dd>You can choose to group the result messages in a <uicontrol>Hierarchical</uicontrol>
              or <uicontrol>Flat</uicontrol> arrangement.</dd>
          </dlentry>
          <dlentry product="authorEclipse developerEclipse editorEclipse" id="dlentry_qcw_bgk_54b">
            <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/MoveDownEntry16.gif"/>Next</uicontrol></dt>
            <dd>Navigates to the message below the current selection.</dd>
          </dlentry>
          <dlentry product="authorEclipse developerEclipse editorEclipse" id="dlentry_rcw_bgk_54b">
            <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/MoveUpEntry16.gif"/>Previous</uicontrol></dt>
            <dd>Navigates to the message above the current selection.</dd>
          </dlentry>
          <dlentry id="dlentry_scw_bgk_54b">
            <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/RemoveSelected16.gif" id="image_zzg_s54_5r"/>Remove
                selected</uicontrol></dt>
            <dd>Removes the current selection from the view. This can be helpful if you want to
              reduce the number of messages, or remove those that have already been addressed or not
              relevant to your task.</dd>
          </dlentry>
          <dlentry id="dlentry_tcw_bgk_54b">
            <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/RemoveAll16.gif" id="image_cy5_lbp_5r"/>Remove
                all</uicontrol></dt>
            <dd>Removes all messages from the view.</dd>
          </dlentry>
        </dl>
      </p>
    </section>
    <section id="results_view_contextual_menu_actions">
      <title>Results View Contextual Menu Actions</title>
      <p id="p_ucw_bgk_54b">The following actions are available when the contextual menu is invoked in this view:</p>
      <p id="p_vcw_bgk_54b">
        <dl id="dl_wcw_bgk_54b">
          <dlentry id="dlentry_xcw_bgk_54b">
            <dt><uicontrol>Learn Word(s)</uicontrol> (Available when spelling errors are reported in
              the Results view)</dt>
            <dd>Adds the word(s) to a list of learned words to instruct the spell checker engine to
              not report the word(s) as spelling errors in the future.</dd>
          </dlentry>
          <dlentry product="editor author developer" id="dlentry_ycw_bgk_54b">
            <dt><uicontrol>Show message</uicontrol></dt>
            <dd>Displays a dialog box with the full error message, which is useful for a long
              message that does not have enough room to be displayed completely in the view.</dd>
          </dlentry>
          <dlentry product="editor author developer" id="dlentry_zcw_bgk_54b">
            <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/MoveUp16.gif" id="image_glw_xw4_5r"/>Previous
                message</uicontrol></dt>
            <dd>Navigates to the message above the current selection.</dd>
          </dlentry>
          <dlentry product="editor author developer" id="dlentry_adw_bgk_54b">
            <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/MoveDown16.gif" id="image_iff_yw4_5r"/>Next
                message</uicontrol></dt>
            <dd>Navigates to the message below the current selection.</dd>
          </dlentry>
          <dlentry id="dlentry_bdw_bgk_54b">
            <dt><uicontrol product="author developer editor"><image
                  href="../img/RemoveSelected16.gif" id="image_sxb_5w4_5r"/>Remove
                selected</uicontrol><uicontrol
                product="authorEclipse developerEclipse editorEclipse">Remove</uicontrol>
            </dt>
            <dd>Removes selected messages from the view.</dd>
          </dlentry>
          <dlentry id="dlentry_cdw_bgk_54b">
            <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/RemoveAll16.gif" id="image_y2s_tw4_5r"/>Remove
                all</uicontrol></dt>
            <dd>Removes all messages from the view.</dd>
          </dlentry>
          <dlentry id="copy-action">
            <dt><uicontrol><image href="../img/Copy16.png" id="image_fhv_5w4_5r"
              />Copy</uicontrol></dt>
            <dd>Copies information associated with the selected messages. For example: <ul id="ul_ddw_bgk_54b">
                <li id="li_edw_bgk_54b" irina="irina">The file path of the document that triggered the output message.</li>
                <li product="editor author developer" id="li_fdw_bgk_54b" irina="irina">The path of the <xref
                    keyref="glossentry_main-file"><term>main file</term></xref> (in the case of
                  a <xref href="validation-scenario.dita#validation-scenario" format="dita"
                    >validation scenario</xref>, it is the path of the file where the
                  validation starts and can be different from the validated file).</li>
                <li id="li_gdw_bgk_54b" irina="irina">Error severity (error, warning, info message, etc.)</li>
                <li id="li_hdw_bgk_54b" irina="irina">Name of validating processor. </li>
                <li product="editor author developer" id="li_idw_bgk_54b" irina="irina">Name of <xref
                    href="validation-scenario.dita#validation-scenario" format="dita">validation
                    scenario</xref>. </li>
                <li id="li_jdw_bgk_54b" irina="irina">The line and column in the file that triggered the message.</li>
              </ul></dd>
          </dlentry>
          <dlentry id="dlentry_kdw_bgk_54b">
            <dt><uicontrol>Copy Description</uicontrol></dt>
            <dd>Copies the description values for all selected items.<ph
                product="author developer editor"> It is possible to <xref
                  href="preferences-menu-shortcut-keys.dita#preferences-menu-shortcut-keys/how_to_assign_a_shortcut_key_or_edit_an_existing_"
                  >assign a shortcut key</xref> for this action.</ph></dd>
          </dlentry>
          <dlentry product="editorEclipse authorEclipse developerEclipse" id="dlentry_ldw_bgk_54b">
            <dt><uicontrol>Show message</uicontrol></dt>
            <dd>Opens a dialog box that displays the details of the message.</dd>
          </dlentry>
          <dlentry product="editor author developer" id="dlentry_mdw_bgk_54b">
            <dt><uicontrol>Select All</uicontrol></dt>
            <dd>Extends the selection to all the messages from the view.</dd>
          </dlentry>
          <dlentry product="editor author developer" id="dlentry_ndw_bgk_54b">
            <dt><uicontrol>Print Results</uicontrol></dt>
            <dd>Sends the complete list of messages to a printer. For each message, the included
              details are the same as the ones for the <xref href="#results-view/copy-action"
                format="dita"><uicontrol>Copy</uicontrol> action</xref>. This action is also
              available in the <menucascade>
                <uicontrol>Window</uicontrol>
                <uicontrol>Results</uicontrol>
              </menucascade> menu.</dd>
          </dlentry>
          <dlentry id="dlentry_odw_bgk_54b">
            <dt><uicontrol>Save Results</uicontrol></dt>
            <dd>Saves the complete list of messages in a file in text format. For each message, the
              included details are the same as the ones for the <xref
                href="#results-view/copy-action" format="dita"><uicontrol>Copy</uicontrol>
                action</xref>.<ph product="author developer editor"> This action is also available
                in the <menucascade>
                  <uicontrol>Window</uicontrol>
                  <uicontrol>Results</uicontrol>
                </menucascade> menu.</ph></dd>
          </dlentry>
          <dlentry id="dlentry_pdw_bgk_54b">
            <dt><uicontrol>Save Results as XML</uicontrol></dt>
            <dd>Saves the complete list of messages in a file in XML format. For each message, the
              included details are the same as the ones for the <xref
                href="#results-view/copy-action" format="dita"><uicontrol>Copy</uicontrol>
                action</xref>.</dd>
          </dlentry>
          <dlentry id="dlentry_qdw_bgk_54b">
            <dt><uicontrol>Save Results as HTML</uicontrol></dt>
            <dd>Saves the complete list of messages in a file in HTML format. For each message, the
              included details are the same as the ones for the <xref
                href="#results-view/copy-action" format="dita"><uicontrol>Copy</uicontrol>
                action</xref>.</dd>
          </dlentry>
          <dlentry product="editor author developer" id="dlentry_rdw_bgk_54b">
            <dt><uicontrol>Group by</uicontrol></dt>
            <dd><ph conkeyref="reusables-editing-documents/group_by_actions"/></dd>
          </dlentry>
          <dlentry conkeyref="reusables-editing-documents/ungroup-all-dlentry"
            product="author developer editor" id="dlentry_sdw_bgk_54b">
            <dt/>
            <dd/>
          </dlentry>
          <dlentry conkeyref="reusables-editing-documents/show-columns-dlentry"
            product="author developer editor" id="dlentry_tdw_bgk_54b">
            <dt/>
            <dd/>
          </dlentry>
          <dlentry conkeyref="reusables-editing-documents/restore-defaults-dlentry"
            product="author developer editor" id="dlentry_udw_bgk_54b">
            <dt/>
            <dd/>
          </dlentry>
          <dlentry id="dlentry_vdw_bgk_54b">
            <dt><uicontrol product="author developer editor"><image href="../img/ExpandAll16.png"
                  id="image_ktt_th3_2s"/>Expand All</uicontrol><uicontrol
                product="authorEclipse developerEclipse editorEclipse">Expand All</uicontrol></dt>
            <dd><ph product="authorEclipse developerEclipse editorEclipse">Available when
                  <uicontrol>Hierarchical</uicontrol> mode is selected. </ph>Expands all the nodes
              of the tree, which is useful when the messages are presented in a hierarchical
              mode.</dd>
          </dlentry>
          <dlentry id="dlentry_wdw_bgk_54b">
            <dt><uicontrol product="author developer editor"><image href="../img/CollapseAll16.png"
                  id="image_djg_5h3_2s"/>Collapse All</uicontrol><uicontrol
                product="authorEclipse developerEclipse editorEclipse">Collapse All</uicontrol></dt>
            <dd><ph product="authorEclipse developerEclipse editorEclipse">Available when
                  <uicontrol>Hierarchical</uicontrol> mode is selected. </ph>Collapses all the nodes
              of the tree, which is useful when the messages are presented in a hierarchical
              mode.</dd>
          </dlentry>
        </dl>
      </p>
    </section>
